<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Strict//EN"
	 "http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-strict.dtd">
<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"
	  xmlns:metal="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/metal"
	  xmlns:tal="http://xml.zope.org/namespaces/tal">
	<head>
		<meta http-equiv="content-type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8" />
		<title>NextThought Account Confirmation</title>
		<style metal:use-macro="options/master/macros/style">
			#green-bar {
			background-color: #89be3c;
			width: 100%;
			height: 5px;
			margin-left: -30px;
			padding-right: 40px;
			}
			#logo-bar {
			margin-top: 20px;
			margin-bottom: 30px;
			}
			body {
			margin-left: 30px;
			margin-right: 0px;
			font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
			font-size: 14pt;
			color: #757474;
			}
			a {
			text-decoration: none;
			color: #3fb3f6;
			}
			.tterm, strong {
			font-weight: bold;
			color: #494949;
			}
			h1, h2, h3, h4, h5, h6 {
			font-weight: bold;
			}
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<div metal:use-macro="options/master/macros/header">
		<div id="green-bar"></div>
		<div id="logo-bar">
			<img src="http://d2ixlfeu83tci.cloudfront.net/images/email_logo.png" width="177" height="25"
			alt="NextThought Logo" />
		</div>
		</div>

		<p>Dear Parent,</p>

		<p>
			Thank you for submitting the consent form
			for <span tal:content="options/profile/realname" class="realname tterm">John Doe</span>
			(username: <span tal:content="options/user/username" class="tterm-color">username</span>).
			We have activated the social features
			for the account. These features, which will allow your child to share
			notes and collaborate with others, will be available the next time
			your child signs in to his or her account and fills out some
			information.
		</p>

		<p>
			We are excited to have your child join the NextThought community, and
			we believe that having access to the interactive content and features
			will both enrich your child's education and provide him or her with a
			more engaging experience.
		</p>

		<p>
			Sincerely,<br />
			NextThought
		</p>

		<p style="font-size: smaller">
			If you feel this email was sent
			in error, or you did not submit a consent form to enable
			social features for your child's account, you may email us
			at <a href="mailto:support@nextthought.com">support@nextthought.com</a>.
		   </p>

	</body>
</html>
